## VMOS PLATFORM QUICK-REF

- **Codebase:** `/home/debian/Downloads/vmos-titan-unified/` (.venv activated)
- **Client:** `from vmos_titan.core.vmos_cloud_api import VMOSCloudClient`
- **Devices:** 100+ cloud instances, 8 local Cuttlefish
- **Auth:** HMAC-SHA256, 3-5s rate spacing, exponential backoff on 110031
- **Device status:** 10=running, 11=booting, 12=resetting, 14=stopped, 15=bricked
- **Never do:** `replacePad`, `updatePadAndroidProp` (both cause reboot)
- **Never do:** `pm disable-user com.cloud.rtcgesture` (permanent Status 11 brick), mass `chmod` on `/sys/block/` (cascading crashes), `mount tmpfs /system/priv-app/` (PM destroyed)
- **Safe property update:** `updatePadProperties` (no restart)
- **Safe tmpfs:** `/dev/.sc` is persistent tmpfs overlay, safe for payload staging

---

## ERROR CODES
| Code | Meaning | Action |
|------|---------|--------|
| 110031 | Rate limit | Backoff 3→5→10→30s |
| 110101 | Timeout | Retry, 30s ceiling |
| 110201 | File transfer | Chunk retry |
| 111001 | Auth fail | Refresh credentials |
| 1104 | Param error | Validate payload |

